---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Partnership | ARM Management"
  description="ARM Management works with a select network of professional partners across the EU, GCC, Asia, and Latin America — built on mutual expertise, shared standards, and complementary capabilities."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560472354-b33ff0c44a43?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Partnership</span>
      <h1>Build Something Together.</h1>
      <p>Professional partnerships built on mutual expertise, shared standards, and complementary capabilities.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Our Approach to Partnership</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Not a Referral Arrangement. A Professional Relationship.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">ARM Management works with a select network of professional partners across the EU, GCC, Asia, and Latin America. Partnership with ARM is not a referral arrangement with a finder's fee — it is a professional relationship built on mutual expertise, shared standards, and complementary capabilities.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">We partner with firms and individuals who advise clients with international business requirements that align with ARM's practice areas. The relationship works when both parties bring genuine expertise and maintain consistent standards of client service. We are selective about the partnerships we form for the same reason we are selective about the clients we serve.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Partnership Types</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">How We Work Together</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>Law Firms &amp; Legal Practices</h3>
          <p>Corporate and commercial law firms whose clients require cross-border entity formation, compliance coordination, or regulatory advisory beyond the firm's core jurisdictions. We provide a seamless extension of your service offering.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Accounting &amp; Tax Advisory Firms</h3>
          <p>Accounting practices and tax advisory firms with clients expanding internationally who require local compliance coordination, entity formation, or regulatory advisory in jurisdictions outside their coverage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>Private Banks &amp; Wealth Managers</h3>
          <p>Private banks and wealth management firms whose clients require operational business advisory — entity formation, payroll, compliance — alongside their financial planning. We handle the business side.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>M&amp;A Advisors &amp; Investment Banks</h3>
          <p>Transaction advisory and investment banking firms requiring cross-border structuring, regulatory compliance, and post-acquisition operational support for their deal clients in new jurisdictions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Real Estate &amp; Investment Platforms</h3>
          <p>Real estate agents, investment platforms, and family office intermediaries whose clients are relocating or investing internationally and require coordinated visa, entity, and compliance support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>Local Expert Networks</h3>
          <p>Jurisdiction-specific lawyers, accountants, and compliance professionals who wish to offer their clients access to a broader international advisory capability while retaining the local relationship.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--navy">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:#B8960C">The ARM Partnership Standard</span>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="color:#F7F3EC">What We Look For.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.78)">ARM Management's reputation is built on consistent quality and honest dealing. We extend that standard to every professional relationship we form. Partnership works when both parties bring genuine expertise, maintain consistent client service standards, and refer mandates they are confident will be well-handled — not because of commercial convenience.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:32px">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Genuine Expertise</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">We partner with professionals who are genuinely expert in their field. We do not build referral networks for volume — we build professional relationships for quality.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Shared Client Standards</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Our clients are introduced to partners we would trust with our own matters. The standard of advice and confidentiality must match what ARM clients already receive from us.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Complementary Coverage</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">The best partnerships fill genuine gaps. We look for partners whose jurisdiction or service coverage complements ARM's without competing with it directly.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Long-Term Orientation</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">We are building relationships, not transaction flows. The right partnership develops over time as both parties better understand each other's clients and capabilities.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Ready to Begin?</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">If you advise clients with international business requirements and believe there is a basis for a professional relationship with ARM Management, we would welcome an initial conversation.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
      <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">Return Home</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
